WEBVTT

00:00:17.344 --> 00:00:20.625
Play your hand, or roll the dice and test your odds out

00:00:21.094 --> 00:00:24.375
No second chance, once you make the call

00:00:24.844 --> 00:00:28.125
Trust the cards, get rid of all the doubts that plague you

00:00:28.594 --> 00:00:31.875
Take your stance, and take your first draw!

00:00:32.109 --> 00:00:34.922
I'll keep you guessing each and every move I take

00:00:34.922 --> 00:00:39.609
You gotta know what is at stake to hit the jackpot

00:00:39.609 --> 00:00:42.422
It's not just pride that I'm putting on the line

00:00:42.422 --> 00:00:46.875
This ain't no game to play, unwind, let's start the show now!

00:00:46.875 --> 00:00:49.219
Dealer, place your bets on me!

00:00:49.219 --> 00:00:51.328
Don't fold this queen,

00:00:51.328 --> 00:00:54.375
oh won't you just believe in me?

00:00:54.375 --> 00:00:56.719
Let's go shoot for twenty-one,

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:58.828
ten, ace, and done,

00:00:58.828 --> 00:01:01.875
it's always in the heart of the cards!

00:01:20.625 --> 00:01:22.266
I'm at the top

00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:24.141
I can't be stopped

00:01:24.141 --> 00:01:26.250
And now I've won it all

00:01:28.125 --> 00:01:29.766
No one I see

00:01:29.766 --> 00:01:31.641
will play with me

00:01:31.641 --> 00:01:37.500
so now I'll start it all again!

00:01:39.375 --> 00:01:41.719
Dealer, place your bets on me!

00:01:41.719 --> 00:01:43.828
Don't fold this queen,

00:01:43.828 --> 00:01:46.875
oh won't you just believe in me?

00:01:46.875 --> 00:01:49.219
Let's go shoot for twenty-one,

00:01:49.219 --> 00:01:51.328
ten, ace, and done,

00:01:51.328 --> 00:01:54.375
it's always in the heart of the cards!
